  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1006731">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1006731/" class="title-link">南怀瑾的《禅宗与道家》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1006731"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1033098/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1033098/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">芥末糊</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2005-10-09"
      class="main-meta">2005-10-09 13:05:28</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1006731_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  作为了解禅宗的历史的书来看，还是不错的。但是显然，南师对于禅宗或佛教较为了解，对于道教，道家的介绍与评论就较为肤浅了。  其实，个人觉得如果对于禅宗的制度能有更多的介绍，可能会更好。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1006731_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1006731_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1043441">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1043441/" class="title-link">哲学的历史</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1043441"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/cineNG/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1150841-21.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cineNG/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">西瓜籽丢了</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2006-05-08"
      class="main-meta">2006-05-08 04:06:31</span>
