    <div class="main review-item" id="6715498">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6715498/" class="title-link">与其说是宗教，不如说是一种文化</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6715498"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/jason0805/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u49658425-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jason0805/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">借痴斋主</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-06-25"
      class="main-meta">2014-06-25 11:02:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6715498_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   读南怀瑾先生写的《禅宗与道家》，让我想起了另一个人另一本书，那就是季羡林的《佛》。两个老先生都是对佛教深有研究，而这种研究是从文化角度进行的，不是从宗教信仰角度。于是在阅读的过程中，我也感觉读到的更多是一种文化而不是信仰的宣传。 小乘佛学的人生观，从出世思...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6715498_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6715498_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
